"guimenuitem></menuchoice> no menú de contexto."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disabling Alarm Monitoring"
msgstr "Desactivar a monitorización das alarmas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can temporarily disable alarm monitoring, which prevents &kalarm; from "
